:"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/35.mp3","time_start":100.69,"time_end":102.76},{"position":36,"content":"So are you working here, or are you a student?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/36.mp3","time_start":102.76,"time_end":106.45},{"position":37,"content":"I started studying at the university a couple of weeks ago,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/37.mp3","time_start":106.45,"time_end":109.91},{"position":38,"content":"and I've got a part-time job for a few hours a week.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/38.mp3","time_start":109.91,"time_end":113.18},{"position":39,"content":"What do you do?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/39.mp3","time_start":113.18,"time_end":114.28},{"position":40,"content":"Well, I've done several different things.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/40.mp3","time_start":114.28,"time_end":116.56},{"position":41,"content":"I've just finished a short-term contract as a courier,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/41.mp3","time_start":116.56,"time_end":119.95},{"position":42,"content":"and now I'm working as a waiter in one of the big hotels.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/42.mp3","time_start":119.95,"time_end":124.5},{"position":43,"content":"That can't leave you much time for studying!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/43.mp3","time_start":124.61,"time_end":126.85},{"position":44,"content":"Oh, it's not too bad.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/44.mp3","time_start":126.85,"time_end":128.41},{"position":45,"content":"I manage to fit it all in.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/45.mp3","time_start":128.41,"time_end":130.04},{"position":46,"content":"What are you studying?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/46.mp3","time_start":130.04,"time_end":131.65},{"position":47,"content":"My ambition is to go into parliament eventually,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/47.mp3","time_start":131.65,"time_end":134.59},{"position":48,"content":"so my major subject is politics.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/48.mp3","time_start":134.59,"time_end":137.43},{"position":49,"content":"That's partly why I think the Youth Council is important and want to be a part of it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/49.mp3","time_start":137.61,"time_end":142.74},{"position":50,"content":"And I suppose you're also taking a minor subject, aren't you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/50.mp3","time_start":142.74,"time_end":146.58},{"position":51,"content":"I know a lot of people study economics too.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/51.mp3","time_start":146.58,"time_end":149.7},{"position":52,"content":"I chose history.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/52.mp3","time_start":149.7,"time_end":151.38},{"position":53,"content":"To be honest, I'm not finding it as interesting as I expected!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/53.mp3","time_start":151.38,"time_end":155.14},{"position":54,"content":"OK, so with your studying and your part-time job,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/54.mp3","time_start":155.37,"time_end":159.55},{"position":55,"content":"do you have time for any other interests or hobbies?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/55.mp3","time_start":159.55,"time_end":162.76},{"position":56,"content":"Well, I spend quite a lot of time cycling -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/56.mp3","time_start":162.76,"time_end":165.78},{"position":57,"content":"both around town to get to university and to work,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/57.mp3","time_start":165.78,"time_end":169.34},{"position":58,"content":"and also long-distance, from here to London, for instance.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/58.mp3","time_start":169.34,"time_end":172.86},{"position":59,"content":"That's pretty impressive!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/59.mp3","time_start":172.86,"time_end":174.85},{"position":60,"content":"Anything else?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/60.mp3","time_start":174.85,"time_end":176.1},{"position":61,"content":"For relaxation I'm also keen on the cinema -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/61.mp3","time_start":176.1,"time_end":179.56},{"position":62,"content":"I used to go at least once a week, but I can't manage to go so often now.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/62.mp3","time_start":179.8,"time_end":184.31},{"position":63,"content":"Right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/63.mp3","time_start":184.37,"time_end":185.38},{"position":64,"content":"Are you sure you'll have enough time for the Youth Council?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/64.mp3","time_start":185.38,"time_end":188.76},{"position":65,"content":"Yes, I've worked out that I can afford to reduce my hours at work, and that will make the time.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/65.mp3","time_start":188.76,"time_end":194.02},{"position":66,"content":"So is there any particular aspect of the Youth Council's work that appeals to you, Roger?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/66.mp3","time_start":194.02,"time_end":199.14},{"position":67,"content":"Well, my sister is blind,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/67.mp3","time_start":199.23,"time_end":201.94},{"position":68,"content":"so I'm particularly interested in working with disabled young people,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/68.mp3","time_start":201.94,"time_end":207.05},{"position":69,"content":"to try and improve the quality of their lives.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/69.mp3","time_start":207.05,"time_end":209.85},{"position":70,"content":"That's great.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/70.mp3","time_start":209.85,"time_end":211.13},{"position":71,"content":"Well, the best way to get involved is to be nominated by some people who you know.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/71.mp3","time_start":211.13,"time_end":216.23},{"position":72,"content":"Right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/72.mp3","time_start":216.23,"time_end":217.09},{"position":73,"content":"Can you tell me how to set about organising that?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/73.mp3","time_start":217.17,"time_end":219.97},{"position":74,"content":"You should talk to Jeffrey, our Elections Officer.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/74.mp3","time_start":220.05,"time_end":223.6},{"position":75,"content":"I can arrange a meeting in the council office with him, if you like.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/75.mp3","time_start":223.6,"time_end":227.48},{"position":76,"content":"Yes, please.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/76.mp3","time_start":227.48,"time_end":228.54},{"position":77,"content":"He'll be here next Monday, if that suits you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/77.mp3","time_start":228.54,"time_end":232.3},{"position":78,"content":"That's the 14th, isn't it?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/78.mp3","time_start":232.3,"time_end":234.52},{"position":79,"content":"Yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/79.mp3","time_start":234.52,"time_end":235.4},{"position":80,"content":"I can manage late afternoon.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/80.mp3","time_start":235.49,"time_end":237.58},{"position":81,"content":"Would you like to suggest a time?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/81.mp3","time_start":237.64,"time_end":239.84},{"position":82,"content":"He generally leaves around 5.30.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/82.mp3","time_start":239.84,"time_end":242.68},{"position":83,"content":"Well, would 4.30 be OK?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/83.mp3","time_start":242.8,"time_end":245.72},{"position":84,"content":"My last class finishes at 4, so I'd have plenty of time to get to your office.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/84.mp3","time_start":246.1,"time_end":250.66},{"position":85,"content":"Right, that's fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/85.mp3","time_start":250.66,"time_end":252.51},{"position":86,"content":"Oh, and could I have a phone number we can contact you on?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/86.mp3","time_start":252.6,"time_end":256.44},{"position":87,"content":"Yes, my mobile number's 07788136711.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/87.mp3","time_start":256.44,"time_end":265.16},{"position":88,"content":"Thank you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/88.mp3","time_start":265.16,"time_end":266.39},{"position":89,"content":"Well, we'll look forward to seeing you next week.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/89.mp3","time_start":266.39,"time_end":269.22},{"position":90,"content":"Thanks very much.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/90.mp3","time_start":269.32,"time_end":270.6},{"position":91,"content":"Goodbye.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/91.mp3","time_start":270.6,"time_end":271.51},{"position":92,"content":"Bye.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-11-test-2-part-1-2023-06-04-16-51-01/92.mp3","time_start":271.51,"time_end":272.53}]}